##In the trunk of a car in Shanghai, and it's happening!

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

By Zhu Yiyi, thepaper.cn

Earlier, there were photos circulating on the Internet, saying that Shanghai had seized a number of people hiding in the trunk of cars and people crossing a highway barrier into Shanghai Jinshan situation. Shanghai police verified that the relevant information is not true, the city's public security organs in the work did not find the relevant situation. (related story: Hide Trunk in Shanghai? Fake)

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Did Not expect two days later, "hide the trunk into Shanghai" really happened!

Shanghai First! A woman found in Shanghai hiding in a car trunk has been quarantined. 01:00

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Police found a woman from a key area in the trunk of a car. Photo courtesy of Songjiang District Police

At around 8:00 am on February 11, police from the Songjiang District Branch of the Shanghai Public Security Bureau seized a woman from a key area in the trunk of a car while carrying out an investigation at the G60 highway public security checkpoint.

After investigation, the woman long-term work in Shanghai, January 22 he returned from Shanghai in key areas of the home for the New Year. In the early morning of February 11, she took a friend's car back to Shanghai and hid in the trunk of the car to avoid being quarantined for 14 days after she heard that Shanghai had implemented very strict control measures at the intersections of various expressways, trying to get away with it. The woman and the body temperature of the vehicle were found to be normal.

The pair have been placed in quarantine since their actions violated the Shanghai Municipal People's Government's circular on the strict implementation of measures to prevent and control the outbreak.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Police found a woman from a key area in the trunk of a car.

Starting from January 27, Shanghai has started epidemic prevention and control measures at provincial border public security checkpoints along the expressway into Shanghai, strictly in accordance with the requirements of "every vehicle must be inspected" . It was the first incident in which a car trunk was concealed from police in Shanghai.

The police remind that it is the legal obligation of every citizen to cooperate with epidemic prevention and control work. In order to safeguard their own health and that of the public and maintain public safety in the city, the majority of citizens enter Shanghai from airports, railway stations and road and waterway crossings, they must cooperate in taking body temperature and declare personal information; people from key areas must consciously accept isolation observation; people from other areas who come to Shanghai or return to Shanghai must declare relevant information by themselves and their units, and strictly implement the corresponding preventive and control measures. With the cooperation of the police and the public, we are sure to win the prevention and control of the epidemic.
